        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Give immediate-release tablets without regard to food..Do not break, crush, dissolve, or divide extended-release tab- lets.• Extended-release tablets should be given without regard to food or with a light meal in evening.",
